rthur</persName><placeName ref="#pmb50">Wien</placeName><date when="1900-06-19" n="01">19. 6. 1900</date></correspAction><correspAction type="received"><persName ref="#pmb10863">Beer-Hofmann, Richard</persName><placeName ref="#pmb34401">Altaussee</placeName><date when="1900-06-20">20. 6. 1900</date></correspAction><correspContext><tei:ref type="belongsToCorrespondence" target="#pmb10863">Beer-Hofmann, Richard</tei:ref><ref subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="1900-05-06_01">Schnitzler, Salten, Salten an Beer-Hofmann, 6. 5. 1900</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="1900-06-20_01">Beer-Hofmann an Schnitzler, 20. 6. 1900</ref></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc><encodingDesc><refsDecl><ab>References to Arthur Schnitzler’s diary online consist of the relevant dates only, 
